Requires pygame (checked with pygame 1.9.1)


changing reward of tile: click with LMB on tile, type new reward and press ENTER
changing reward of all non terminal tiles: click with LMB on button "reward", type new reward, press ENTER
setting tile as (non)terminal: hover mouse over tile and press SPACE
setting tile as (non)passable: hover mouse over tile and press RMB
showing arrows pointing best strategy: click with LMB button named arrows

